                <note rend="inline" type="source">882.6176 F 51/195: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Liberia</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Wharton</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Monrovia</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1926-01-28T12:00:00-00:44">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 28, 1926—noon</hi>
                        </date>.<lb/>[Received 5:56 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>4. Rubber agreements ratified by Legislature. Loan ratified with modifications
                    will be cabled.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Wharton</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
